571
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:50,120
Master Fan, her master is--

572
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:52,240
Eat more.

573
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:54,360
All right, I will.

574
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:55,760
Please forgive me, Master Fan.

575
00:29:55,840 --> 00:29:59,240
My master leads a reclusive life.

576
00:29:59,320 --> 00:30:00,680
He has a strange temper.

577
00:30:00,760 --> 00:30:02,560
I'm not allowed to say his name.

578
00:30:03,480 --> 00:30:04,320
Master Fan,

579
00:30:04,400 --> 00:30:07,000
there are different kinds of people
in the martial arts world.

580
00:30:07,080 --> 00:30:08,360
It's understandable, right?

581
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:09,400
Yes.

582
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:13,680
Do you have any family?

583
00:30:16,040 --> 00:30:16,920
No.

584
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:18,520
I'm an orphan

585
