590
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:35,640
It's all right.
You don't have a family now.

591
00:30:35,720 --> 00:30:36,760
But in the future,

592
00:30:36,840 --> 00:30:39,560
you can dedicate yourself
to one of your own.

593
00:30:42,560 --> 00:30:44,400
It's a pity that the timing is not right.

594
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:46,120
If we don't have to seal off the mountain,

595
00:30:46,200 --> 00:30:47,160
I'll choose a day

596
00:30:47,240 --> 00:30:49,200
for you to get married

597
00:30:49,280 --> 00:30:50,960
after the Spring Festival.

598
00:30:55,040 --> 00:30:57,560
Master Fan,
why do we seal off the mountain?

599
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:00,360
Have some dinner first.

600
00:31:00,440 --> 00:31:02,080
Ah Xiang, have some more.

601
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:03,760
Yes, eat up.

602
00:31:09,600 --> 00:31:10,840
I did have an affair

603
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:12,600
with Tragicomic Ghost, Luo Fumeng.

604
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:15,200
At that time,

605
00:31:15,280 --> 00:31:17,840
she was the princess of the Neon Palace

606
00:31:17,920 --> 00:31:21,840
and I was only a poor boy from
the declining branch of the Zhao family.

607
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:25,600
Her family opposed our marriage

608
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:28,000
and grounded her.

609
00:31:29,600 --> 00:31:30,960
She sent me

610
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:35,560
this bloodletter at that time…

611
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:39,240
to show me her decision.

612
00:31:42,480 --> 00:31:43,360
You two…

613
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:46,800
once loved each other.

614
00:31:49,120 --> 00:31:50,720
Then why did you fail her?

615
00:31:51,960 --> 00:31:54,200
It was because of that vicious Li Yao.

616
00:31:55,160 --> 00:31:56,040
Mother?

617
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:59,280
I told you
that you aren't allowed to call her that!

618
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:01,120
She was just a wench!

619
00:32:02,760 --> 00:32:04,720
You don't know what she did to me!

620
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:11,840
GREAT AMBITIONS

621
