623
00:32:17,520 --> 00:32:19,480
I'm the one who should be blamed

624
00:32:19,560 --> 00:32:20,880
for not refusing her in time.

625
00:32:21,640 --> 00:32:22,720
So when

626
00:32:24,160 --> 00:32:27,680
Fumeng and I were about to overcome
all the difficulties

627
00:32:27,760 --> 00:32:29,160
and get married,

628
00:32:31,600 --> 00:32:34,880
she threatened me with my involvement

629
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:36,800
in stealing in the armory.

630
00:32:37,840 --> 00:32:39,360
She demanded that I must go with her

631
00:32:40,080 --> 00:32:41,560
and break up with Fumeng.

632
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:44,440
Xie'er.

633
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:49,840
If I was the only one behind that,

634
00:32:50,600 --> 00:32:52,880
I would not compromise.

635
00:32:53,640 --> 00:32:55,120
But it involved so many people

636
00:32:55,680 --> 00:32:57,800
and I couldn't get my friends in trouble.

637
00:32:58,880 --> 00:33:02,240
So I endured this humiliation

638
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:04,480
and married into her family.

639
00:33:05,440 --> 00:33:07,040
Godfather, do you know that

640
00:33:08,320 --> 00:33:09,640
on the day of your wedding,

641
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:14,280
Luo Fumeng went crazy
and slaughtered the entire Neon Palace?

642
00:33:16,800 --> 00:33:18,120
Do you know

643
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:20,760
why no one has heard of her since then?

644
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:25,960
It was because I tried so hard to find her

645
00:33:26,440 --> 00:33:30,280
and sent her to the Healer Valley
for treatment.

646
00:33:31,800 --> 00:33:33,840
But when I was trying to subdue her,

647
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:36,040
I was badly hurt by her.

648
00:33:37,480 --> 00:33:40,160
I can't make any progress
in martial arts since then.

649
00:33:41,160 --> 00:33:42,960
I've ruined her life.

650
00:33:44,520 --> 00:33:45,640
If it wasn't for me,

651
00:33:46,680 --> 00:33:48,520
she wouldn't end up

652
00:33:48,600 --> 00:33:50,800
in such a poor condition like this.

653
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,360
Xie'er.

654
00:33:58,120 --> 00:33:59,760
This is

655
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:02,920
the most painful memory

656
00:34:04,680 --> 00:34:07,560
and the biggest humiliation of my life.

657
00:34:12,159 --> 00:34:14,840
I planned to take it to my grave.

658
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:17,560
But since you want to know,

659
00:34:20,679 --> 00:34:22,040
I'm telling you about it now.

660
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:24,960
There's another reason

661
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:27,080
for hiding it from you.

662
00:34:29,159 --> 00:34:31,480
I killed Li Yao as well.

663
00:34:35,840 --> 00:34:36,920
I knew it.

664
00:34:39,320 --> 00:34:41,000
I was obedient and loyal,

665
00:34:41,080 --> 00:34:43,719
but not anymore.

666
00:34:44,679 --> 00:34:46,280
The Zhao Jing in front of you

667
00:34:47,120 --> 00:34:51,040
is someone who killed his wife,

668
00:34:51,560 --> 00:34:53,600
murdered his brothers,

669
00:34:53,679 --> 00:34:55,760
and scourged the world.

670
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:58,160
Someone who shall not be forgiven.

671
00:34:59,240 --> 00:35:01,280
The world has failed me

672
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:05,320
and I shall do the same to the world.

673
00:35:08,200 --> 00:35:09,920
But to you…

674
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,400
My son…

675
00:35:17,560 --> 00:35:20,080
The old me has died.

676
00:35:21,720 --> 00:35:24,200
But if I were to keep some kindness

677
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:26,840
and affection for my family,

678
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:30,800
they are for you.

679
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:34,920
This is the last piece of purity
in my life.

680
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:38,000
Promise me

681
00:35:39,560 --> 00:35:40,840
that you will guard it well.

682
00:35:43,480 --> 00:35:45,920
Do not abandon it.

683
00:35:47,880 --> 00:35:48,800
Godfather.

684
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:51,400
It's my fault.

685
00:35:52,640 --> 00:35:54,360
I shouldn't have asked you this.

686
00:35:54,440 --> 00:35:55,840
I won't ask again.

687
00:35:57,800 --> 00:35:58,800
Xie'er,

688
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:01,440
you should know that

689
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:04,320
you are the only one I have

690
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:07,720
and I'm the only one you have.

691
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:19,920
"You won't fail me

692
00:36:20,560 --> 00:36:21,920
and I won't fail you."

