00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:24,320
"You won't fail me

694
00:36:26,040 --> 00:36:27,520
and I won't fail you."

695
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:39,120
Master.

696
00:36:43,560 --> 00:36:45,000
Don't call me that.

697
00:36:46,080 --> 00:36:48,520
Don't you have a new master already?

698
00:36:53,720 --> 00:36:55,000
How did it go?

699
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:58,480
Did you find an answer?

700
00:37:00,200 --> 00:37:01,280
He said

701
00:37:03,040 --> 00:37:04,160
it was his wife, Li Yao,

702
00:37:04,240 --> 00:37:05,840
who threatened him
with the secret of the armory.

703
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:13,400
I can't believe

704
00:37:14,160 --> 00:37:17,400
that his ability to make up stories
is still as good.

705
00:37:18,160 --> 00:37:20,840
It was my father who threatened him first.

706
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:23,520
Why did he frame Li Yao?

707
00:37:24,160 --> 00:37:26,120
Because he killed Li Yao after that.

708
00:37:31,720 --> 00:37:35,920
Li Yao was just a stupid girl.

709
00:37:37,240 --> 00:37:40,560
Although we were rivals in love,

710
00:37:41,800 --> 00:37:43,720
I didn't hate her.

711
00:37:45,400 --> 00:37:46,800
If I was the one

712
00:37:47,600 --> 00:37:49,800
who married Zhao Jing,

713
00:37:52,080 --> 00:37:54,440
the skeleton buried in the ground

714
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:57,480
would be me instead.

715
00:37:59,720 --> 00:38:01,160
"He dallied with me

716
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:04,720
and he forsook me in the end."

717
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:08,800
I gave up everything for Zhao Jing.

718
00:38:09,480 --> 00:38:11,600
But I couldn't believe

719
00:38:12,680 --> 00:38:15,520
that he went for Li Yao, a high-born girl.

720
00:38:17,920 --> 00:38:21,240
My father saw me cry all day

721
00:38:22,240 --> 00:38:24,280
and he couldn't bear it,

722
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:27,560
so he threatened Zhao Jing
with the secret of the armory

723
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:30,800
and lured him with the position
of the chief of the Neon Palace.

724
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:33,800
That's why Zhao Jing had to marry me.

725
00:38:34,680 --> 00:38:36,320
But I didn't expect

726
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:38,760
that he would be so ruthless.

727
00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:40,920
He conspired
with the traitors of Neon Palace

728
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:43,560
and slaughtered all the people

729
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:46,160
on the day of our wedding.

730
00:38:47,200 --> 00:38:48,120
Master.

731
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:50,240
It wasn't you?

732
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:54,160
The past can't be verified.

733
00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:57,520
Neither of you has any solid proof.

734
00:38:58,160 --> 00:39:00,480
If he is indeed as cold-blooded
as you said he is,

735
00:39:01,560 --> 00:39:02,880
why would he spare your life?

736
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:04,280
