737
00:39:05,000 --> 00:39:07,440
keep and cherish your bloodletter?

738
00:39:09,040 --> 00:39:10,240
You really…

739
00:39:11,040 --> 00:39:14,440
You really don't understand Zhao Jing.

740
00:39:15,160 --> 00:39:17,920
Do you know that all his life,

741
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:20,920
he is most proud

742
00:39:21,440 --> 00:39:23,760
of his ability to fool everyone?

743
00:39:24,800 --> 00:39:27,080
He keeps one trophy

744
00:39:27,720 --> 00:39:29,840
for each of his plots.

745
00:39:29,920 --> 00:39:31,400
I'm guessing that

746
00:39:32,200 --> 00:39:34,240
he has his master's ring

747
00:39:35,040 --> 00:39:36,920
and the sword that poisoned Rong Xuan.

748
00:39:38,040 --> 00:39:39,440
If you don't believe me,

749
00:39:39,960 --> 00:39:41,680
go and check it for yourself.

750
00:39:44,040 --> 00:39:45,240
There should be

751
00:39:46,960 --> 00:39:50,120
something left
by that stupid girl, Li Yao.

752
00:39:51,600 --> 00:39:54,440
It's very likely to be their love token.

753
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:58,600
If I'm not wrong,

754
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:02,920
Zhao Jing has also given you

755
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:04,880
a special token

756
00:40:05,440 --> 00:40:07,120
to prove his sincerity.

757
00:40:07,840 --> 00:40:08,800
Am I right?

758
00:40:25,440 --> 00:40:27,400
Master Wen,
tomorrow is the winter solstice.

759
00:40:27,480 --> 00:40:29,280
Will Master Ye be back in time?

760
00:40:29,920 --> 00:40:32,480
Yes, tomorrow is the winter solstice.

761
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:33,920
Shall we make dumplings?

762
00:40:34,520 --> 00:40:35,360
Master Ye said

763
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:36,920
he wanted dumplings
with cabbage and pork stuffing.

764
00:40:37,640 --> 00:40:39,720
What else do you know besides eating?

765
00:40:40,520 --> 00:40:41,920
Master Ye requested it in his letter.

766
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:44,840
Besides, I've worked so hard every day.

767
00:40:44,920 --> 00:40:46,080
Why can't I have some?

768
00:40:46,160 --> 00:40:48,240
You little brat, how dare you talk back?

769
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:49,800
Be careful what you're learning!

770
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:52,200
All right.

771
00:40:52,280 --> 00:40:53,960
I'll buy some ingredients tomorrow.

772
00:40:54,040 --> 00:40:55,440
What else do you want?

773
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:58,320
You're going to listen to him this time?

774
00:40:59,560 --> 00:41:01,280
That Old Monster is getting older.

775
00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:03,760
It's not easy for him to go through
such a long journey to help us.

776
00:41:04,320 --> 00:41:05,520
I'm just going to give him

777
00:41:05,600 --> 00:41:07,120
what he wants to eat.

778
00:41:07,200 --> 00:41:08,480
That's reasonable.

779
00:41:08,560 --> 00:41:10,280
But he has a big appetite,

780
00:41:11,560 --> 00:41:14,480
so we should prepare a lot more food.

781
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:16,440
The liquor is not good either.

782
00:41:16,920 --> 00:41:19,040
How about this, Lao Wen?

783
00:41:19,120 --> 00:41:21,280
Hire a carriage to Qingshui Town

784
00:41:21,360 --> 00:41:23,120
and buy some good food and liquor.

785
00:41:23,200 --> 00:41:24,080
All right.

786
00:41:24,160 --> 00:41:25,400
Mr. Wen, I'll go with you.

787
00:41:25,480 --> 00:41:26,640
Go where?

788
00:41:26,720 --> 00:41:28,360
One round trip takes a whole day.

789
00:41:28,440 --> 00:41:31,000
Don't even think about it.
Stay and practice your martial arts.

790
00:41:31,080 --> 00:41:32,280
That's not fair.

791
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:33,560
I have never slacked off.

792
00:41:34,160 --> 00:41:35,560
You're still talking back?

793
00:41:35,640 --> 00:41:36,840
Go to bed now.

794
00:41:38,080 --> 00:41:39,360
Lao Wen.

795
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:40,600
Get some rest.

796
00:41:40,680 --> 00:41:42,520
Shall we chat a while longer?

797
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:45,280
And have some drinks?

798
00:41:46,640 --> 00:41:47,800
I'll pass.

799
00:41:48,360 --> 00:41:50,800
We'll have a fierce battle soon.

800
00:41:51,920 --> 00:41:53,920
We need to have a good rest.

801
00:41:55,440 --> 00:41:56,280
That's right.

802
00:41:57,120 --> 00:41:58,160
Go to bed then.

803
00:42:00,240 --> 00:42:01,600
Let's go, Chengling.

804
00:42:06,800 --> 00:42:07,640
Let's go.

805
00:42:21,760 --> 00:42:23,160
GENTLE WINDS AND LIGHT CLOUDS

